Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:08.23,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(590,200)\fad(800,800)}幹\N勁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.10,0:00:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.67,0:00:06.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼了  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.47,0:00:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是各種沒幹勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.77,0:00:09.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼傻話呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:14.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們可是高中生哦  而且還是新學期哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.24,0:00:17.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹勁什麼的只要去做就自然會有的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.99,0:00:20.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是連「去做」的幹勁都拿不出來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.58,0:00:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼樣才能拿出「去做」這樣的幹勁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.68,0:00:27.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「去做」的幹勁嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.60,0:00:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…  總之就得去幹！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.03,0:00:31.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:38.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想做一個單純的笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.91,0:00:50.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  差不多該起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:54.16,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(90,300)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N1
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.60,0:01:06.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.35,0:01:09.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的早飯是烤魚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.80,0:01:12.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  我要吃蛋包飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.62,0:01:14.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天不是吃過了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.93,0:01:17.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魚裡面可是有大量營養的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:23.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑食的話可是長不大…啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.92,0:01:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  那可是我們重要的早飯
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.34,0:01:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  不…不是那樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.42,0:01:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可絕對不是機器人般的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.78,0:01:40.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.68,0:01:41.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.29,0:01:42.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:47.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.07,0:01:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定那隻貓也有著自己的難處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.75,0:02:09.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要撞上了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}小芥子人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:03:57.28,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}小芥子人偶（こけし）江戶時代末期開始出現的日本東北地區的溫泉特產及鄉土玩具\N一般形態為球形頭部和圓柱形身子，沒有四肢。
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}紅牛玩偶
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.57,0:03:59.62,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}紅牛玩偶（赤べこ）福島縣會津地區的鄉土玩具，「べこ」是東北方言「牛」的意思\N整體塗紅，頭部會擺動，是祝願小孩子茁壯成長的吉祥物。
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.59,0:04:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)\c&H0F0F0F&\bord0\fs35}鮭魚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:04.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Selamat pagi:印尼語早上好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:12.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  祐子  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.69,0:04:16.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  我忘記帶學生證了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.54,0:04:18.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  Selamat pagi被無視了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.37,0:04:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不想被高年級學生叫出去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:26.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種時候  只要說「我是三年級學生」不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可解決不了問題
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.57,0:04:33.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  打雷？  明明是晴天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.48,0:04:35.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會突然掉下什麼東西來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.42,0:04:37.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像是雷陣雨  冰雹之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:41.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小芥子人偶…從天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧  祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.75,0:04:46.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會是小芥子人偶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.37,0:04:50.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚇我一跳  這是從哪兒掉下來的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.38,0:04:52.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道啦  
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.31,0:04:56.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  在人生中被小芥子人偶砸到的幾率很小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.04,0:04:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎沒有不是嗎  那樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接近於零了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.91,0:05:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反過來說  也許會走運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走運個頭啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會是紅牛玩偶啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.99,0:05:15.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅牛玩偶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對  並不是沒有走運
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.86,0:05:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣想就行了  美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.40,0:05:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有被生鮮的東西砸到真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:25.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想來  那可真是不幸中的萬幸…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是鮭魚啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.70,0:05:51.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.77,0:05:53.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.66,0:05:58.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.93,0:06:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat pagi
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:01.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.98,0:06:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你在看什麼書
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,房地產的情報雜誌
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.16,0:06:07.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  麻衣要搬家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.04,0:06:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.28,0:06:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎  Selamat pagi又被無視了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:18.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法 今天要在之後唱搖籃曲了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.10,0:06:19.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.92,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Selamat malam:印尼語晚上好的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:22.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Selamat malam
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.26,0:06:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.45,0:06:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  你應該說Selamat pagi才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.39,0:06:33.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是  什麼語言？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:38.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班…班會要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.35,0:06:46.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  今早來學校的時候  發現這個在鞋箱裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.37,0:06:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有誰知道是誰放進去的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.67,0:06:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個  要是有誰知道的話  請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.23,0:07:01.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  會是誰呢  
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.38,0:07:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做那種事的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.86,0:07:04.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會不會是惡作劇呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.49,0:07:07.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定是喜歡老師的學生之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:10.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不會放彌勒菩薩的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.37,0:07:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛  我也不是無法瞭解那種暗戀的仰慕之情啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:17.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像美緒對笹原學長的思念一樣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.04,0:07:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混…混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.37,0:07:40.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.73,0:07:46.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士一定在擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:49.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小炭爐點著火放在那裡也很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個  下不去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.18,0:08:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  筷子不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木屐也不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.42,0:08:13.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.16,0:08:16.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  聯手也沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.11,0:08:21.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我會被別人發現是機器人的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.79,0:08:31.59,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,300)\fad(800,0)\fs25}W\No\Nn\Nd\Ne\Nr\Nf\Nu\Nl
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.38,0:08:29.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.12,0:08:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.07,0:08:55.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼  再不快點吃的話就要打午休鈴了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:58.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  你不喜歡吃小香腸嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呼呼呼…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:05.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃便當的時候把最美味的留在最後這是基本常識哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.90,0:09:09.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是用「美味」作結束語
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.54,0:09:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來  我要開動啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.15,0:09:17.33,title-W,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(70,290)\fad(800,800)}日\N常\N之\N2
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.94,0:09:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.81,0:09:52.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿過去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.55,0:09:53.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.83,0:10:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還早得很呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.56,0:10:11.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.34,0:10:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.81,0:10:15.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.62,0:10:18.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.35,0:10:26.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上壘
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:29.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…出局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:34.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  美緒  三秒規則哦  三秒規則
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:37.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你那是徹徹底底出局了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.76,0:10:44.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美味！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子是笨蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.13,0:10:58.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先出石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.84,0:11:00.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後出布
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.63,0:11:02.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿出你滿滿的能量喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石頭剪刀布！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.67,0:11:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.90,0:11:21.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}甩繩者頭戴的是中之條家的大福頭套
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.15,0:11:16.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.28,0:11:26.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.55,0:11:30.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進入春季  新的一年就開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.71,0:11:33.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,氣候還在持續寒冷中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.52,0:11:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是比同學們要冷得多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.22,0:11:41.65,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(490,160)\fad(600,0)}日常之3
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.07,0:11:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之希望大家不要感冒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.99,0:11:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎  這是大家與校長我的約定
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:53.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果大家不聽我的話  校長我就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.61,0:11:58.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去別的學校當別人的校長了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:05.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:07.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼  交頭接耳會被批評的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:13.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那什麼  校長沒有意識到自己的冷笑話太老土了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.76,0:12:19.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都沒有人笑  他自己應該是最清楚的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  難講呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.87,0:12:26.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是想把  明知道大家沒有笑還在不斷努力的姿態
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.32,0:12:28.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現給現在的年輕人們看嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:31.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是那樣  
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.94,0:12:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位校長…就太厲害了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.37,0:12:44.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非是對那種老頭兒冷笑話…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.11,0:12:51.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我是第一次看到麻衣笑得這麼厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.56,0:12:54.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  這裡讓我來吐槽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.14,0:12:55.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.98,0:12:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.85,0:13:01.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.94,0:13:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在有種一開口就會失去一切的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.57,0:13:07.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.95,0:13:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.20,0:13:24.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在她發現之前…還是不要拿下來好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.94,0:13:26.53,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}觸手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.52,0:13:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼接下來有請櫻井老師為大家進行輔導
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.65,0:13:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻井老師  交給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  櫻井老師
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.44,0:13:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.09,0:13:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  我是學生輔導員櫻井
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.74,0:13:51.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.28,0:13:58.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然在這麼多人面前會緊張的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.49,0:14:01.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行  這樣下去的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.39,0:14:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多久都無法接近我成為理想中的教師的目標了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.68,0:14:07.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說的時候  就要一股腦兒說出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.48,0:14:08.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.73,0:14:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近在學校經常看到山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.66,0:14:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請大家不要把山羊帶到學校來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.11,0:14:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山羊  山羊有什麼錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.38,0:14:29.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎山羊來上學並沒有違反校規不是嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.99,0:14:32.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  啊  那個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.10,0:14:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒  那不是笹原學長嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.48,0:14:39.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:44.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚  那就…那就允許騎山羊來上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,駁回啦  駁回
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.43,0:14:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部駁回！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.96,0:14:55.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼能夠帶山羊來上學
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.46,0:14:58.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別那樣說  立花美里呀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:02.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何我要用我尊貴的雙足走著上學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:05.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了  笹原家的長男可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:07.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笹原家的長男算什麼玩意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.13,0:15:10.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們家不過是普通農家罷了不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣  長男說自己是長男有什麼不對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:18.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  笹原家裡原來是農家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.87,0:15:21.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有種被騙了的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻停在自行車場的山羊  原來是笹原學長帶來的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.12,0:15:31.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎著白色山羊的笹原學長…來迎接我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:43.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  new  year
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.57,0:15:46.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me  Me too
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美緒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  邊騎自行車邊打手機是非常危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.07,0:16:01.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要那樣做
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…最後
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.60,0:16:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天早上我在自己的鞋箱裡發現了彌勒菩薩像
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.34,0:16:11.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我認為這種惡作劇是不可取的行為
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.73,0:16:13.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  借過一下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.86,0:16:15.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒菩薩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.68,0:16:18.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻衣  請不要突然停下來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.20,0:16:26.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這處  說不定就是所謂的既視感
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.79,0:16:28.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰做的？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:31.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會生氣的  請舉起手來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.62,0:16:34.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒有人承認的話  今天的早會就一直開下去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.23,0:16:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:38.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你站出去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.98,0:16:50.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀  因為我聽說今天是櫻井老師的生日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀哎呀  是這麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:56.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彌勒菩薩像是不行的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:08.07,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}5-7-5的俳句格式
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.05,0:17:02.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本以為會很適合  而送出禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.28,0:17:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果彌勒菩薩像  被完全拋棄  by校長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.69,0:17:17.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼早會到此結束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝我們校長至今為止的努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.79,0:17:23.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教導主任！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.65,0:17:29.25,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(60,250)\fad(600,800)}按\N鈕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.46,0:17:31.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個消防栓的按鈕看上去很有想去按的魔力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:34.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  噗噗噗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:39.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你試著按一下吧  之前按的時候沒有發出聲音呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒  真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:42.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火災
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.91,0:17:43.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.92,0:17:45.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦  要逃出去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:47.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  總之先到學校空地上去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.05,0:17:52.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙推什麼推啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你在推我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.60,0:17:54.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.41,0:17:56.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我以前早就看你這傢伙不順眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:59.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別吵了  也許會有人死掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:17:59.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先逃了再說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吵等下再吵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.90,0:18:09.27,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}Helvetica Standard：日常原作者あらゐけいいち以自己的同人社團「ヒマラヤイルカ」的\N名義創作的同人志2009年8月23日發行，內容為WEB日記漫畫「Helvetica Standard」的總集篇。
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.47,0:18:12.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.79,0:18:17.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請問KY是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.53,0:18:21.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  KY到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:26.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  請告訴我KY方面的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}誰來救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.19,0:18:27.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.98,0:18:31.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  隊長  KY是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.65,0:18:33.25,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}KY為空気が読めない的略寫，即不解風情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.89,0:18:43.66,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(660,340)\fad(300,0)\fs30}重\N要\N的\N事\N與\N該\N做\N的\N事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.28,0:18:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年B班笹原幸治郎同學  請火速到辦公室富岡老師處來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.50,0:18:48.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說確實是沒有違反校規
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是山羊也太那什麼了吧  山羊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.37,0:18:53.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有別的辦法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.03,0:18:56.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意徒步的話  騎自行車也是可以的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.63,0:18:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要不是山羊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.44,0:18:59.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.33,0:19:00.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫富岡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,富岡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請加上老師
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.43,0:19:08.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你就不能不叫它山羊  叫它笹原小次郎嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:16.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在它還是羊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.50,0:19:22.94,title-B,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(50,290)\fad(600,0)}日\N常\N之\N4
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.66,0:19:23.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名字叫做東雲名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.75,0:19:27.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是和我一起生活的博士製造出的機器人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.01,0:19:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士好像在進行著某種研究  整天都待在家裡
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:39.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我照顧著博士  度過著每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.88,0:19:45.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  牛奶沖好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:51.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有什麼出眾的功能卻有痛覺的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.19,0:19:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃  你怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.47,0:19:58.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博…博士  碰到小趾了  碰到小趾了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:20:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小趾…趾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之這樣就應該沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.02,0:20:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.46,0:20:14.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有出眾的功能小趾卻能摘下來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:23.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,博士  這個發條是什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.05,0:20:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈  還沒有轉過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.22,0:20:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時會轉轉看
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.93,0:20:32.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要這樣轉的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.04,0:20:34.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  會怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:43.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  看來我有很多出眾的功能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.80,0:20:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧  很有趣對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:49.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非就只是為了這個而裝了發條…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.15,0:20:54.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非就只是為了這個而裝了發條？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.19,0:20:55.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.22,0:20:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把發條取下來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.45,0:20:57.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.14,0:20:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.27,0:21:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為裝了發條很可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.18,0:21:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是認真的  請馬上摘下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:04.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒…明明很可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.17,0:21:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要是能變得更加普通就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.05,0:21:10.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能像普通人一樣坐在椅子上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:13.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡覺的時候可以隨意翻身
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話  連學校都沒法去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不做成人形機器人就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名乃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.32,0:21:24.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.36,0:21:31.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙你的  我是騙你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.53,0:21:34.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦  博士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:35.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.98,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}也就是芥川龍之介賞，是為了紀念日本文豪芥川龍之介而設立的文學獎項
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.30,0:21:37.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去給我拿個芥川獎來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.18,0:21:39.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要芥川獎  我要芥川獎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.36,0:21:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs24}就是這樣的日常風景
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.73,0:21:52.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好  我是名乃的大拇趾
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.59,0:23:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,容量為1GB
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.55,0:23:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好的容量大小呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.62,0:23:39.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請期待下回的日常第二話
